breakpoints 
(1) mobile device           max-width:576px 
(2) mobile device (fold)    min-width:576px
(3) tablet device           min-width:768px 
(4) mini leptop             min-width:992px 
(5) normal leptop           min-width:1200px = 1140
(6) large screen            min-width:1400px  

